dons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/profiles_green/","description":"Green","fullDescription":null,"weeklyDownloads":128,"type":"theme","creator":{"name":"Firefox","url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/user/4757633/"},"developers":[],"screenshots":[{"url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/user-media/version-previews/full/4058/4058782.png?modified=1754665333","width":680,"height":92,"thumbnailURL":"https://addons.mozilla.org/user-media/version-previews/thumbs/4058/4058782.png?modified=1754665333","thumbnailWidth":473,"thumbnailHeight":64},{"url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/user-media/version-previews/full/4058/4058783.svg?modified=1754665333","width":720,"height":92,"thumbnailURL":"https://addons.mozilla.org/user-media/version-previews/thumbs/4058/4058783.jpg?modified=1754665333","thumbnailWidth":720,"thumbnailHeight":92}],"contributionURL":"","averageRating":5,"reviewCount":0,"reviewURL":"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/profiles_green/reviews/","updateDate":1754683526000},{"id":"passbolt@passbolt.com","icons":{"32":"https://addons.mozilla.org/user-media/addon_icons/687/687753-32.png?modified=15ac2013","64":"https://addons.mozilla.org/user-media/addon_icons/687/687753-64.png?modified=15ac2013","128":"https://addons.mozilla.org/user-media/addon_icons/687/687753-128.png?modified=15ac2013"},"name":"Passbolt - Open source password manager for teams","version":"5.11.1","sourceURI":"https://addons.mozilla.org/firefox/downloads/file/4757551/passbolt-5.11.1.xpi","homepageURL":"https://www.passbolt.com","supportURL":"https://www.passbolt.com","amoListingURL":"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/passbolt/","description":"Passbolt is an open source password manager designed for collaboration. Securely create, manage and monitor your passwords. Share them instantly with your team.","fullDescription":"Passbolt is an open source password manager designed for collaboration. You can securely generate, store, manage and monitor your team credentials.\n\nGet access to all of your logins and passwords from multiple browsers or even your mobile phone. Create strong random passwords, thanks to the fully customizable password generator, and share them instantly with your team.\n\nPassbolt is built on top of an open API made for developers and agile teams. Passbolt is extensible and yet usable by everyone. No technical knowledge is required to use it.\n\nThis is why Passbolt is trusted by small businesses, as well as government offices, regulated industries, and privacy-conscious organizations:\n\nBoost collaboration & productivity:\n- Easily share one password, or a folder with a single user or a group of users;\n- Use personal or shared tags to identify passwords and secrets;\n- Give specific access rights to a user or group;\n- Get detailed reporting on access & change history.\n\nSecurity by design. Audited and certified:\n- True end-to-end encryption;\n- Interoperable cryptography based on OpenPGP;\n- Full control your own encryption key;\n- Access revocation that actually works;\n- Regularly audited by independent auditors.\n\nMade in Europe.  Privacy by default:\n- Host it in our cloud, located in Europe;\n- Or self-host it for full data ownership;\n- No tracker, no strings attached.\n\nPassbolt source code comes under an AGPL license (yes even the commercial version) and is publicly available. You are free to audit it, contribute to it, or redistribute it.\n\nThis add-on is required to use the software, in order to provide advanced security features as well as functionality such as password auto filling on web pages.\n\nGet started now:\nhttps://www.passbolt.com/cloud/signup\n\nCheck out the source code:\nhttps://github.com/passbolt","weeklyDownloads":801,"type":"extension","creator":{"name":"passbolt","url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/user/12112545/"},"developers":[],"screenshots":[{"url":"https://addons.mozilla.org/user-media/previews/full/318/318435.png?modified=1744290209","width":2400,"height":